pr_title: Added shell script for setting up local environment
pr_body:
Shell script automates the task of installing all required dependencies required to replicate lab.mlpack.org environment in our local machine.

Supports:
- [x] - Creating new conda environment & installing dependencies.
- [x] - Upgrading dependencies in existing conda environment.

Usage:
```
$ wget -q https://raw.githubusercontent.com/davidportlouis/examples/env_setup/install.sh
$ chmod a+x install.sh
$ ./install.sh <environment name of your choice>
```
